.DT
set_respond_to_with
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
set_respond_to_with

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_respond_to_with -  This method sets the current responses for the npc.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void set_respond_to_with(mixed map)
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/living/response_mon.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method sets the current responses for the npc.
This will overwrite the current responses in the npc.
Please use add_respond_to_with in your NPC's instead of
this function call, as it requires prior knowledge as to
the internal structure of the respond_to_with code that
add_respond_to_with handles nicely.
The array is of the formant:
.EP
.SP 5 5
  ({
.EP
.SP 5 5
     trigger1,
.EP
.SP 5 5
     response1,
.EP
.SP 5 5
     trigger2,
.EP
.SP 5 5
     response2,
.EP
.SP 5 5
     ...
.EP
.SP 5 5
   })
.EP
.SP 5 5

.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
add_respond_to_with(), query_respond_to_with()

.EP

